flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Monthly, quarterly, and mid-term capacity planning cycles.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve demand forecasts]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Allocate capacity based on forecasts]
  N2 --> N3[Stream: STREAMS - Validate build plans against constraints]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Analyze medium-term capacity gaps]
  N4 --> N5{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Review and update assumptions}
  N5 -->|Primary| N6[PB: Remote Functions - Adjust build plans if necessary]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, improved OTIF, synchronized cross-plant and cross-supplier capacity planning.]
  N5 -->|Identified capacity shortfall| B1[Trigger build plan adjustment workflow]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Updated build plans]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Supplier capacity commitment mismatch| B2[Notify stakeholders]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Resolved capacity issues]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Infeasible build plan| B3[Request manual review]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Approved or revised build plan]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]